trans:
No reservations for cards or albums.
No reservations for items or product that has limited quantities.
Unable to reserve = No charges.
Reserved but cancel = Full reservation charged.
For other inquiries, please DM us.
Steps for booking a slot: Contact via DM.
Once the details are fully release = You can message us immediately.
1. We respond in order of the message received.
2. Do not send additional messages, because it will push you message to the top of the queue.
3. There is a specific time to reply. If you don't respond within the timeframe the slot will be given to the next person.
- Priority is given to returning customers who have previously left us reviews. When booking, use the same account to contact us.
- If you would like to use your review privilege, please make sure your account is not locked as some reviews won't appear in the tag.
Some slots may be uncertain and will only accepted closer to the reservation date.
For fully book events or to who didn't get the queue = Will not be answering DM.
A deposit is required to prevent cancellation.
When do we accept bookings?
Event tickets, concerts, and fan meetings:
Slots will be opened after the official announcement of date, time, and event structure are fully released.
Prices will vary based on difficulty
Form filling, other bookings.
